Title: More feat. Anderson .Paak
Description: ['Music video directed by Shinichiro Watanabe for the single ', More (feat. Anderson .Paak), ' by American record producer Flying Lotus (Steven Ellison). It is featured on his sixth studio album "Flamagra." Flying Lotus and Shinichiro Watanabe\'s creative kinship was cultivated while working on Blade Runner: Black Out 2022, and the mutual respect led them to collaborating on this video.', '\n', '\n']
